---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - Claude News" lang="en" showSidebar={false}>
  <div class="privacy">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="effective">Effective date: March 6, 2026</p>

    <p>OTTFStudio ("Operator") operates Claude News (<a href="https://claude-news.today">claude-news.today</a>). This policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you subscribe to our newsletter.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Data</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Retention</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Email address</td><td>Newsletter delivery</td><td>Until unsubscribe</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Language preference (ko/en/ja)</td><td>Send briefings in selected language</td><td>Until unsubscribe</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>Your information is used solely for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Sending AI news briefings about Claude Code and Anthropic</li>
      <li>Processing subscription confirmation (Double Opt-in)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Third-Party Data Processing</h2>
    <p>We use the following service to process and deliver emails:</p>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Processor</th><th>Location</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Brevo (Sendinblue)</td><td>France (EU)</td><td>Email delivery and subscriber management</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p>Brevo complies with GDPR. Your data is used exclusively for newsletter delivery.</p>

    <h2>4. Cookies, Analytics, and Advertising</h2>
    <p>This site uses or may use the following tools for service improvement, usage analysis, and advertising.</p>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Tool</th><th>Data Collected</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Google Analytics 4</td><td>Page visits, browser info, approximate location</td><td>Usage statistics</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Advertising platforms (Google Ads, etc.)</td><td>Cookie-based interests, browsing history</td><td>Personalized ads and ad performance measurement</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p>These tools use cookies to collect usage data. You can disable or delete cookies in your browser settings, though some features may be limited. For details on data processing, see <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

    <h2>5. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Newsletter subscription</strong>: Your consent (Article 6(1)(a) GDPR)</li>
      <li><strong>Usage analytics</strong>: Legitimate interest in service improvement (Article 6(1)(f) GDPR)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Unsubscribe</strong>: Click the "Unsubscribe" link at the bottom of any email.</li>
      <li><strong>Data deletion</strong>: Email <a href="mailto:privacy@claude-news.today">privacy@claude-news.today</a> to request deletion of your data.</li>
      <li><strong>Access and correction</strong>: Contact us at the same email address.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>For EU residents: You have the right to access, rectify, erase, restrict processing, and port your data under GDPR. You may also lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority.</p>

    <h2>7. Data Deletion</h2>
    <p>When you unsubscribe, your email address is removed from our mailing list on Brevo. For explicit deletion requests, we will process them without undue delay.</p>

    <h2>8. Contact</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Operator: OTTFStudio</li>
      <li>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@claude-news.today">privacy@claude-news.today</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>Any changes to this policy will be posted on this website.</p>

    <p class="back"><a href="/">&larr; Back to Claude News</a></p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .privacy {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }
  .effective {
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .back {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }
</style>
